    "Details": "As the Inner Sphere developed Omnimech technology in the 3050s, the Taurian Concordat watched with interest. Finally, in the early 3060s, thanks to some good old-fashioned corporate espionage, the Concordat managed to steal basic Omnimech technology plans from the Federated Suns and developed their own Omnimech, the Liberty. To keep costs low, the Liberty is made with simple off-the-shelf weapons technology. The Liberty Prime is armed with twin PPCs, a LRM-15, two Medium Lasers, and 4 Small Lasers. Endo-Steel and an XL Engine provide the weight for the payload.<br><br>X-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
